    <a href="/pages/auto-social" data-xyla-card="auto-social"><h3>Auto Social</h3><p>Shopify content automation for Xyla AI, image reuse, video prompts, and campaign drafts.</p><span>Open Workflow</span></a>
    <a href="/pages/brand-partners" data-xyla-card="brand-partners"><h3>Brand Partnerships</h3><p>Creator, campaign, and product surfaces for brands and content partners.</p><span>Start Partnership</span></a>
    <a href="/pages/image-library" data-xyla-card="image-library"><h3>Image Library</h3><p>Human-readable page plus JSON manifest for automation systems.</p><span>View Library</span></a>
